text: Otto Bærentzen (31 May 1868 - 20 May 1943) was a Danish fencer. He competed at the 1920 and 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1868 births Category:1943 deaths Category:Danish male fencers Category:Olympic fencers of Denmark Category:Fencers at the 1920 Summer Olympics Category:Fencers at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Frederiksberg
